{"type":"message","id":"98d277d6","parentId":"9b43715c","timestamp":"2026-04-12T11:53:49.080Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user sent an image showing search results for \"echotik\" on clawhub.1688.com. It shows two tools:\n1. Echotik Product Search - for TikTok Shop product data analysis\n2. Echotik New Product Rank - for TikTok Shop new product rankings\n\nThey seem to be looking at ClawhHub (which appears to be a skill marketplace for OpenClaw based on the URL). Let me analyze the image and respond appropriately.\n\nThe image shows they're on clawhub.1688.com and searched for \"echotik\" - getting results for two EchoTik-related skills/tools for TikTok Shop data analysis.\n\nI should acknowledge what I see and ask what they need help with regarding these tools."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我看到了！你在 ClawHub 上搜索 **EchoTik** 相关的技能工具。\n\n图片显示两个 EchoTik 选品数据工具：\n\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **Echotik 商品搜索** | 一键分析 TikTok Shop 商品数据（销量、佣金、网红带货数据） |\n| **Echotik 新品榜单** | 快速发现 TikTok Shop 新品榜单 |\n\n这些正好是你需要的 TikTok Shop 数据源！🎯\n\n你是想：\n1. **让我帮你安装这些工具/技能？**\n2. **想了解如何使用这些工具进行选品？**\n3. **还是其他需求？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775994821754,"responseId":"062abac5c360d8744366880b77441120"}}
