{"type":"message","id":"f7a55fe5","parentId":"272f13e0","timestamp":"2026-04-12T11:53:52.738Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-12 19:53:50 GMT+8] Feishu[tts] DM | ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68 [msg:om_x100b528c373a8100c10b68f047f30ab]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b528c373a8100c10b68f047f30ab\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sun 2026-04-12 19:53 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n这些skill 是不是组合后基本不需要咱们之前的浏览器自动化了。 就差最后一步 妙手采集可能还需要浏览器操作"}],"timestamp":1775994832736}}
{"type":"message","id":"f451c9d0","parentId":"f7a55fe5","timestamp":"2026-04-12T11:54:06.183Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about whether these skills (EchoTik tools) would eliminate the need for browser automation. They're noting that the last remaining step - 妙手采集 (Miaoshou ERP collection) - might still need browser operation.\n\nLooking at the context from SOUL.md and TOOLS.md:\n- EchoTik API is listed as \"待配置\" (to be configured) for getting Thailand/Vietnam TikTok hot sale rankings\n- 妙手/店小秘 is listed as \"待配置\" (to be configured) for ERP product following/collection\n\nThe user is essentially asking if installing these EchoTik skills would automate most of the data collection workflow, reducing the need for manual browser automation.\n\n\nBased on the tool descriptions, EchoTik can pull product data, sales metrics, and influencer performance directly through the API, while the new product rankings feature provides trend insights. The main remaining piece is 妙手采集, which handles bulk ERP operations and might require browser access to interact with the ERP system directly."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 是的，你说得对！\n\n**有了 EchoTik 技能后：**\n- ✅ 商品搜索、销量分析、网红带货数据 → **API 直接拉取**，不用浏览器\n- ✅ 新品榜单、类目榜单 → **API 直接拉取**，不用浏览器\n\n**还可能需要浏览器的场景：**\n- ⚠️ 妙手/店小秘 ERP → 养号、采集搬家（1688→TikTok）→ 大概率还是需要浏览器\n- ⚠️ 竞品监控（某些平台没开放 API）→ 可能需要偶尔看一眼\n\n**总结：** 数据分析 80-90% 的工作可以 API 化，妙手采集是最后一个浏览器节点。\n\n要我帮你安装 EchoTik 这两个技能吗？安装好后我们可以开始配置 API 密钥，然后测试一下数据拉取流程 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775994832738,"responseId":"062abad102d318b962cc92612b565eaa"}}
